    dc:description "FIGURE 1. (a), (b) and (c), Photographs of male holotype of Mantidactylus paidroa (ZSM 1777 / 2008) in life (SVL 22.3 mm), in dorsolateral and ventral views." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202729/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.202730>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Sonagrams and oscillograms of parts of a series of double notes, recorded from the holotype of Mantidactylus paidroa on 24 January 2008; (a) fragment of the call with 8 double notes; (b) enlarged view of two double notes." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/202730/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

